    EMA equation is 
        EMA(today) = (Value today* (smoothing 1 + days )) + EMA yesterday * (1-(smoothing/1+days);

Buy Strategy 2:
If RSI is below 30 twice could be a buy zone.

Buy Strategy 3:
if ask price bounces off moving averages with wicks, buy zone.



Sell Strategy 

Sell Strategy 1:
